    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你被派去探索夜间的一座神秘建筑。只有你的经理会支持你，其余的你必须自己做。找到月球并尝试活着返回。单人或与朋友一起玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176210/extras/9d7e78f1ff2414725f49ccbab49d18e6.poster.avif?t=1742872216\" width=610 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176210/extras/9d7e78f1ff2414725f49ccbab49d18e6.webm?t=1742872216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176210/extras/9d7e78f1ff2414725f49ccbab49d18e6.mp4?t=1742872216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各种令人毛骨悚然的怪物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单独玩或与在线公司（最多 4 人）或分屏多人游戏（最多 2 人）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个变化多端的大型地点，有很多探索。探索该区域并完成任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176210/extras/f0197cdd6632f883a6de2b8f70598dfb.poster.avif?t=1742872216\" width=610 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176210/extras/f0197cdd6632f883a6de2b8f70598dfb.webm?t=1742872216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176210/extras/f0197cdd6632f883a6de2b8f70598dfb.mp4?t=1742872216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理资源：查找、移动、修复、连接、观察。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过游戏中的语音聊天在线交流。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏由一个人开发。</p><p cl